			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Go to CTY_Main_A 8; 26; -93 with only one avatar (in order no to trigger a dialog between an avatar and gale companion when leaving dialog)\r\n\r\n2) Buy The Annals of Karsus: A Netherese Folly from her\r\n\r\n3) Leave the dialog, which will trigger the PAD"
				},
